title: Cat Power - Speaking For Trees (a film by Mark Borthwick) -
description:
&#039;Speaking For Trees: A Film by Mark Borthwick&#039; centers a nearly 2-hour long film of Cat Power playing solo outdoors in the countryside. The experimental filmmaker and visual artist shot it from a great distance in gloriously grainy color, and recorded with all the ambient sounds of nature. This cinema verite piece, in the tradition of Warhol and Wiseman, is a fascinating document.

this is an ultra rare dvd
